Javascript XML : is a syntax extinsion to JavaScript

WHy JSX : 
    React Embraces the fact that rendering logic should be coupled with UI
    Helpful as a visual aid when working with UI inside JavaScript
    React separates concerns instead of separating technology
    it also allows React to show more useful errors and warning messages

What I learn this Section ?

Basic syntax of JSX
